Bayer Abandons Molecular Imaging Unit Sale, FT Deutschland Says

-- B y   S h e e n a g h   M a t t h e w s
-- 
2011-12-06T06:47:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-06/bayer-abandons-molecular-imaging-unit-sale-ft-deutschland-says.html
Bayer AG (BAYN)  has abandoned the planned
sale of its molecular imaging unit,  Financial Times Deutschland 
said, citing unidentified people from the industry.  None of the interested parties handed in a bid for the
unit, which employs 100 people, the German newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sheenagh Matthews in Frankfurt at 
 smatthews6@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
